<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Dear&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Contact_First_Name__c}&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Contact_Last_Name__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Thank you for visiting our CTI {!Outbound_Notification__c.Preferred_Campus__c}&nbsp;campus on&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Current_Date__c}.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">We are really excited that you are considering us as your preferred Higher Education&nbsp;Institution.<br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">As a reminder, here is what we discussed:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">To secure your registration please submit the following documentation and make the following payment&nbsp;as soon as possible so that we can process your&nbsp;student number:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>R800 registration fee (non-refundable)</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Completed and signed registration form</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Signed payment calculator</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Signed Addendum A</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Signed Social Indemnity form&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>A copy of student’s ID (or passport if foreign student)</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">•<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>A copy of sponsor’s ID (or passport if foreign student)</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">You are welcome to deposit the R800 registration fee into our bank account and fax the deposit slip, together with all the above registration documentation, to me on&nbsp;{!Outbound_Notification__c.Preferred_Campus_Fax__c}. Please contact me in order to confirm that I have received all documentation after it has been sent. Faxed and e-mailed documentation will be accepted; however the originals must be submitted upon enrolment. </font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1"><br></font></div><div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Account Name: CTI Education Group</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Bank: Standard Bank</font></div><div><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans-Serif" size="1">Account Number:&nbsp;</font><font face="Verdana,Helvetica,Sans